We used our DePCRM program developed earlier (88) to predict CRE and CRMs in the genome based on the motifs found in all datasets or sub-datasets with minor modifications. Briefly, for each pair of motifs Md(i) and Md(j) found in the same dataset d, we compute a motif co-occurring score Sc defined as,
